.SS "11.5. How do I highlight all the non-printable characters in a file?"
.IX Subsection "11.5. How do I highlight all the non-printable characters in a file?"
You can use the following commands and search pattern to highlight all the
non-printable characters in a file:
.PP
.Vb 2
\& :set hlsearch
\& /\e(\ep\e|$\e)\e@!.
