.IX Subsection "11.8. How do I search for a word without regard to the case (uppercase or lowercase)?"
To always ignore case while searching for a pattern, set the 'ignorecase'
option:
.PP
.Vb 1
\& :set ignorecase
.Ve
.PP
To ignore case only when searching a particular pattern, use the special \ec
directive:
.PP
