.IX Subsection "11.9. How do I search for words that occur twice consecutively?"
You can use one of the following search commands to locate words that occur
twice consecutively:
.PP
.Vb 2
\&  /\e(\e<\ew\e+\e)\e_s\e+\e1\e>
\&  /\e(\e<\ek\e+\e)\e_s\e+\e1\e>
.Ve
