.IX Subsection "12.2. How do I replace all the occurrences of multiple consecutive space characters to a single space?"
You can use the following command to replace all the occurrences of
multiple consecutive space characters to a single space:
.PP
.Vb 1
\& :%s/ \e{2,}/ /g
