.SS "12.4. How do I delete all blank lines in a file? How do I remove all the lines containing only space characters?"
.IX Subsection "12.4. How do I delete all blank lines in a file? How do I remove all the lines containing only space characters?"
To remove all blank lines, use the following command:
.PP
.Vb 1
\& :g/^$/d
.Ve
.PP
To remove all lines with only whitespace (spaces or tabs) in them, use the
following command:
.PP
.Vb 1
\& :g/^\es\e+$/d
.Ve
.PP
To remove all the lines with only whitespace, if anything, use the
following command:
.PP
.Vb 1
\& :g/^\es*$/d
.Ve
